OL,3,CWhat is Awaab's Law?
OL,5,FA new law to force landlords to fix
OL,6,Fdangerous damp and mould issues has
OL,7,Fcome into effect, following the death
OL,8,Fof a two-year-old boy.
OL,10,FSocial housing landlords in England
OL,11,Fwill face court action and
OL,12,Fcompensation orders from Monday 27
OL,13,FOctober if they fail to improve
OL,14,Fconditions for tenants quickly under
OL,15,FAwaab's Law.
