OL,3,CWhat is Awaab's Law?
OL,5,FThe legislation is named after Awaab
OL,6,FIshak, who died in 2020 from a
OL,7,Frespiratory condition caused by
OL,8,Fprolonged exposure to mould in the
OL,9,Fsocial home his family rented in
OL,10,FRochdale, Greater Manchester.
OL,12,FThe toddler's death caused outrage and
OL,13,Fprompted the law that requires
OL,14,Flandlords to fix reported hazards in
OL,15,Fsocial housing faster, and rehouse
OL,16,Ftenants in safe accommodation if
OL,17,Fnecessary.
OL,19,FWhat do landlords now have to do?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
