OL,3,CWhat is Awaab's Law?
OL,5,FLandlords will have to investigate and
OL,6,Ffix dangerous damp and mould within 10
OL,7,Fworking days of being notified, and
OL,8,Frepair all emergency hazards within 24
OL,9,Fhours of reporting.
OL,11,FIf homes cannot be made safe within
OL,12,Fthe timeframes, alternative
OL,13,Faccommodation must be offered to the
OL,14,Fresidents.
OL,16,FLandlords will also be required to
OL,17,Fconsider the circumstances of tenants
OL,18,Fwhich could put them at risk such as
OL,19,Fhaving young children or disabilities.
