OL,3,CWhat is Awaab's Law?
OL,5,FLandlords who fail to comply risk
OL,6,Fbeing taken to court.
OL,8,FThe law will be strengthened over
OL,9,Ftime, and from 2027 it will require
OL,10,Flandlords to fix all dangerous hazards.
OL,12,FHow many people will it affect?
OL,14,FAlmost a quarter of people with issues
OL,15,Fof damp, mould, or cold in their
OL,16,Fhomes, are social renters, a survey
OL,17,Fhas suggested.
