OL,3,CWhat is Awaab's Law?
OL,5,FAs the rules come into force in
OL,6,FEngland, a UK-wide survey found 23% of
OL,7,Fthose who said they had issues such as
OL,8,Fdamp, mould, or condensation in their
OL,9,Fhomes were social renters, while 21%
OL,10,Fwere in private rented accommodation.
OL,12,FWill it be extended?
OL,14,FCampaigners are calling for the new
OL,15,Frequirements for social landlords to
OL,16,Fbe applied urgently to the privately
OL,17,Frented sector.
